    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "——不对！",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Ema001.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "sfx",
      "params": {
        "path": "/Audio/SFX/Scenario/Sfx_Scenario_001 Wake up.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "bg",
      "params": {
        "path": "/Background/Stills/RGB/Still_490_001.png",
        "subId": "Middle",
        "posX": 80,
        "posY": -35,
        "scale": 3,
        "rotZ": -10
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "animate",
      "params": {
        "target": "Stills-Middle",
        "props": {
          "posX": 60,
          "posY": -20
        },
        "easing": "EaseOutBack",
        "duration": 0.4
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "bg",
      "params": {
        "path": null,
        "subId": "Overlay",
        "tint": "#000000",
        "duration": 1.2
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "wait",
      "params": {
        "time": 0.2
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "樱羽艾玛大喊着，爬起身来。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "大概是因为做了噩梦，她的呼吸相当紊乱，\n而且满身都是汗水。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "原来是做梦。她才刚安下心来——\n眼前的光景就逐渐清晰了起来。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "bgm",
      "params": {
        "path": "Bgm_21_1"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "咦，怎么回事，这里是……？",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Ema002.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "bg",
      "params": {
        "path": "/Background/Stills/RGB/Still_490_001.png",
        "posX": 50,
        "posY": 50,
        "rotZ": 0,
        "duration": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "resetText",
      "params": {}
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "hide",
      "params": {
        "id": "Stills-Middle"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "wait",
      "params": {
        "time": 0.8
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "醒来的艾玛发现，这里不是她自己的房间。\n这是张做工粗糙的双层床，她睡在了这里的下铺。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "床紧贴着老旧的石墙，\n而石墙似乎透着一股寒气，总令人不禁为之一颤。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "室内光线昏暗，空气也并不畅通。\n并且——有一道铁栅栏限制了自由。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "牢、牢房……！？为什么！？",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Ema003.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "艾玛陷入了恐慌，\n拼命回想着睡前的记忆。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "（昨天是想到明天我就要上高中了……\n 很开心地睡着了才对）",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Ema004.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "昨天是春假的最后一天。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "艾玛早早地洗了澡，换了睡衣，\n早早地钻进了被窝里。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "（记得睡觉前……我还看着挂在墙上的\n 全新的高中制服）",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Ema005.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "望着那件明天就要穿上的制服，\n艾玛露出了十分幸福的笑容。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "（还下了决心，一切要重头来过……）",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Ema006.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "然后在温暖的被窝包裹下，闭上了双眼。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "可是现在，她正被关在牢房里。\n身上还穿着自己从没见过的衣服。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "（这是噩梦的后续……？）",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Ema007.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "但，四周的一切却如此真实。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "她大致观察了下室内。四周被结实的石墙包围，\n只有铁栅栏一面联通着过道。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "墙上安装有电视屏幕。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "在透着中世纪气息的古牢里面，\n这块现代随处可见的显示屏幕实在是格格不入。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "bg",
      "params": {
        "path": "/Background/MainBackground/RGB/Background_001_001.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Ema",
        "appearance": [
          "Surprised1"
        ],
        "position": 50
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "我说，这里究竟是什么地方！？",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Ema008.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "艾玛抓着铁栅栏，喊出声来。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "紧接着，远远地从其他地方传来了\n其他少女们的叫喊声。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "hideChars"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "竟把本小姐关在这种地方！\n究竟是什么意思啊！？",
      "speaker": "???",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Unknown001.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "监禁少女可是犯罪欸！虽然不知是谁，\n可干出来这种事，这辈子就到头了欸！？",
      "speaker": "???",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Unknown002.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "喂，开什么玩笑，我要杀了你！放我出去！！",
      "speaker": "???",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Unknown003.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Ema",
        "appearance": [
          "Normal1",
          "ArmR3"
        ],
        "position": 50
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "（……太好了，被关进来的\n 不止我一个人）",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Ema009.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "现场忽然吵闹起来，\n艾玛的脸上露出了安心。紧接着——"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "hideChars"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "——能不能给我安静一下？",
      "speaker": "???",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Unknown004.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "从艾玛身后冷不防传来一道清冽的声音。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "sfx",
      "params": {
        "path": "/Audio/SFX/Scenario/Sfx_Scenario_001 Wake up.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "艾玛顺着声音望去，\n发现双层床的上铺有个刚起身的人。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Hiro",
        "appearance": [
          "Angry1"
        ],
        "position": 50
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "大吵大闹是不对的。",
      "speaker": "???",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Unknown005.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "——！！",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Ema010.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "艾玛十分吃惊，瞬间忘记了呼吸。\n因为，她认识这位说话的少女。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "（真的假的……\n 是二阶堂希罗……？）",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Ema011.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "二阶堂希罗——"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "是在艾玛的初中时代，令她深陷黑暗的同窗，\n也是广受众人仰慕，常在人群中心可爱地微笑着的少女……"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Hiro",
        "appearance": [
          "Surprised1"
        ],
        "position": 50
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "和她对上眼的希罗，也大大的瞪圆了眼睛。\n艾玛还是第一次见有人把眼睛瞪得那么大。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "为什么你会在这里？",
      "speaker": "二阶堂希罗",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Hiro001.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "sfx",
      "params": {
        "path": "/Audio/SFX/Scenario/Sfx_Scenario_178 Landing sound.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "希罗轻快的爬下了床，向艾玛问道。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "往日同窗竟出现在眼前，\n惊慌失措的艾玛哑口无言。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "hideChars"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Hiro",
        "appearance": [
          "Surprised1"
        ],
        "position": 30
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Ema",
        "appearance": [
          "Fearful1",
          "ArmR3"
        ],
        "position": 70
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "啊……",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Ema012.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "这是哪里？",
      "speaker": "二阶堂希罗",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Hiro002.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "希罗四下张望着，\n紧张地尖声问道。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "我、我说，希罗……",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv02/0101Adv02_Ema013.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "艾玛鼓起勇气，\n尝试向往日旧识搭话。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "hideChars"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "这时——"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "sfx",
      "params": {
        "path": "/Audio/SFX/Scenario/Sfx_Scenario_003 Monitor.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "声音从墙壁上的显示屏幕传来。\n艾玛和希罗吓了一跳，然后望向屏幕。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "resetText",
      "params": {}
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
